00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:51,640
 Now, what we see in Genesis 1, 2 is this perfect picture

301
00:11:51,640 --> 00:11:54,200
 of the Spirit hovering over what the Bible describes

302
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:57,840
 as a formless void, a dark creation.

303
00:11:57,840 --> 00:12:00,440
 And we said in week one that what the Spirit is doing

