00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:02,720
 in hovering over it is having this desire

305
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:05,560
 to take something that is formless,

306
00:12:05,560 --> 00:12:09,920
 bring it into form, and then move it to fullness.

