00:16:56,760 --> 00:16:59,360
 Then God instructs him to take the tablets

423
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:01,280
 and place them in a box,

424
00:17:01,280 --> 00:17:03,860
 quite literally the Ark of the Covenant.

