00:17:03,860 --> 00:17:06,160
 Now, this is funny because so often as Christians

426
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:08,140
 we're trying to get the Spirit out of a box,

427
00:17:08,140 --> 00:17:11,600
 but here at this moment, God puts the Spirit in a box.

428
00:17:11,600 --> 00:17:13,080
 Now why does he do this?

429
00:17:13,080 --> 00:17:17,020
 It's because he wants the Spirit to be with his people.

430
00:17:17,020 --> 00:17:20,960
 But because of sin, there still needs to be a barrier

431
00:17:20,960 --> 00:17:23,580
 between God and his holiness and God's people.

432
00:17:23,580 --> 00:17:25,680
 So he's placed within this box,

