00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:29,720
 and his presence now goes forward with his people.

434
00:17:29,720 --> 00:17:31,240
 And because his presence is with his people,

435
00:17:31,240 --> 00:17:33,480
 their character is there, the people are created

436
00:17:33,480 --> 00:17:35,800
 and made holy, not because they were perfectly holy

437
00:17:35,800 --> 00:17:39,260
 themselves, but because God's presence was amongst them.

438
00:17:39,260 --> 00:17:42,040
 But it's in a box because there are boundaries.

439
00:17:42,040 --> 00:17:44,020
 And if anybody was to open that box,

440
00:17:44,020 --> 00:17:46,120
 if anyone was to carry that box in the wrong way,

441
00:17:46,120 --> 00:17:47,680
 if anybody was to do something,

442
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:49,940
 then they would be kind of completely punished

443
00:17:49,940 --> 00:17:52,320
 because that box was a sacred thing

444
00:17:52,320 --> 00:17:53,480
 carrying the presence of God,

445
00:17:53,480 --> 00:17:55,640
 and there was boundaries still between humanity

446
00:17:55,640 --> 00:17:56,740
 and his presence.

447
00:17:56,740 --> 00:17:59,620
 But he had drawn nearer, you following?

448
00:17:59,620 --> 00:18:03,000
 This becomes even more so when you see the next movement.

449
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:06,040
 The box then gets placed eventually into the temple.

450
00:18:06,040 --> 00:18:08,140
 So David, Solomon, with the vision that they have

451
00:18:08,140 --> 00:18:10,200
 for the temple and the construction of the temple,

452
00:18:10,200 --> 00:18:13,880
 then the box placed in the heart of the temple itself.

453
00:18:13,880 --> 00:18:15,920
 And as it's placed in there, it's placed in this place

454
00:18:15,920 --> 00:18:17,560
 called the Holy of Holies.

455
00:18:17,560 --> 00:18:20,400
 And the Holy of Holies was like the inner sanctum

456
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:22,160
 of where the spirit of God was,

457
00:18:22,160 --> 00:18:24,920
 where the Ten Commandments and the Ark of the Covenant sat.

458
00:18:24,920 --> 00:18:26,880
 And in the Holy of Holies, it was separated,

459
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:30,040
 again, from the people, with a large, thick curtain.

460
00:18:30,040 --> 00:18:31,960
 And once again, only one person could go

461
00:18:31,960 --> 00:18:33,240
 into the presence of God.

462
00:18:33,240 --> 00:18:34,860
 And this was the priest once a year

463
00:18:34,860 --> 00:18:37,400
 who had completely purified himself for that journey

464
00:18:37,400 --> 00:18:38,940
 to go into God's presence.

465
00:18:38,940 --> 00:18:41,240
 So there again, God's presence is with his people,

466
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:43,920
 but there's a boundary still that separates

467
00:18:43,920 --> 00:18:46,960
 the holiness of God and his people themselves.

468
00:18:46,960 --> 00:18:52,760
 As God's people are taken into exile because of their sin,

469
00:18:52,760 --> 00:18:54,600
 and Assyria and Babylon come and do that

470
00:18:54,600 --> 00:18:56,840
 and bring them into exile, the temple,

471
00:18:56,840 --> 00:18:58,760
 the first temple is destroyed.

472
00:18:58,760 --> 00:19:00,140
 And when the temple is destroyed,

473
00:19:00,140 --> 00:19:01,280
 here's what happens to Israel.

474
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:02,640
 They're wondering about the spirit,

475
00:19:02,640 --> 00:19:04,680
 and they say, where is the spirit?

476
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:05,920
 Where has the spirit gone?

477
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:08,400
 Because of our brokenness and our sin, we're now in exile.

478
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:09,580
 The temple's been destroyed.

479
00:19:09,580 --> 00:19:12,840
 God's presence has left us.

480
00:19:12,840 --> 00:19:15,320
 And when 70 years later, they're actually released back,

481
00:19:15,320 --> 00:19:17,300
 and Zerubbabel brings a group of them back

482
00:19:17,300 --> 00:19:19,340
 to start to rebuild the temple,

483
00:19:19,340 --> 00:19:21,000
 they want to rebuild the temple.

484
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:22,780
 They create the Holy of Holies again.

485
00:19:22,780 --> 00:19:25,300
 The presence of God again falls amongst this curtain,

486
00:19:25,300 --> 00:19:27,380
 but there's a change in the thinking of Israel

487
00:19:27,380 --> 00:19:28,460
 at this point.

488
00:19:28,460 --> 00:19:30,620
 And they think, look, every single time we try

489
00:19:30,620 --> 00:19:33,460
 to restore our relationship with the presence

490
00:19:33,460 --> 00:19:35,880
 and the spirit of God, it doesn't seem to work.

491
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:39,380
 Perhaps only God can do that work.

492
00:19:39,380 --> 00:19:42,300
 And so at this period, although they rebuild the temple,

493
00:19:42,300 --> 00:19:43,880
 and God's presence comes back,

494
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:45,660
 their thinking is slightly different.

495
00:19:45,660 --> 00:19:49,180
 They're like, God will need to step in in the future

496
00:19:49,180 --> 00:19:51,300
 if ever humanity and the spirit

497
00:19:51,300 --> 00:19:53,120
 will ever reconcile together again.

498
00:19:53,120 --> 00:19:57,360
 And then comes Jesus.

499
00:19:57,360 --> 00:20:00,220
 Jesus, as we know, is the Messiah, the incarnation,

500
00:20:00,220 --> 00:20:02,420
 fully God and fully human.

501
00:20:02,420 --> 00:20:04,260
 And here's what I want you to think about that.

502
00:20:04,260 --> 00:20:09,260
 This is the fullness now of the spirit in a human person.

503
00:20:09,260 --> 00:20:11,540
 The incarnation is this beautiful idea

504
00:20:11,540 --> 00:20:13,560
 that the spirit is no longer in a bush,

505
00:20:13,560 --> 00:20:16,000
 it's no longer in a mountain, it's no longer in a box,

506
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:19,720
 it's no longer in a temple, it's now come in a person.

507
00:20:19,720 --> 00:20:21,600
 And it's come in the fullness of a person

508
00:20:21,600 --> 00:20:24,460
 so that the spirit and humanity are now this picture

509
00:20:24,460 --> 00:20:25,760
 of reconciliation.

510
00:20:25,760 --> 00:20:28,360
 But note, it's still just one person.

511
00:20:28,360 --> 00:20:32,400
 And Jesus, in living out the fullness of the spirit

512
00:20:32,400 --> 00:20:36,260
 within him, does the amazing external manifestations

513
00:20:36,260 --> 00:20:39,920
 that we see, commands nature, walks on water,

514
00:20:39,920 --> 00:20:42,260
 does the things, heals people, multiplies food,

515
00:20:42,260 --> 00:20:45,220
 does crazy stuff through the power of the spirit.

516
00:20:45,220 --> 00:20:47,140
 And as he begins to walk out the kingdom,

517
00:20:47,140 --> 00:20:49,300
 he begins to demonstrate what that kingdom

518
00:20:49,300 --> 00:20:52,300
 could actually look like when the fullness of the spirit

519
00:20:52,300 --> 00:20:54,020
